Design Subscription based billing for Online Image Service


  • All users should be able to upload the image for global range
  • All users should be able to view the image
  • Subscribed users can only download images
  • Images should support as many formats and resolution as possible for download(only subscribed users)
  • Users can search for images based on text.

Non Functional Requirements

  • Consistency >> Availability for buying subscription downloads (Billing)
  • Availability >> Consistency for view images.
  • Scalable
  • Low Latency for view. (10s of ms)
  • Image should be visible with 5-10 min of upload

API / Interface

  1. User should be able to upload the image.
  2. Uer should be able to View the image.
  3. User should be able to subscribe.
  4. Subscribed user should be able to download.

Load Balancer
API Gateway
1. Routing
2. Authn / Authz
3. Rate Limiting

SQL DB
Postgress Image Metadata DB

get the images based on 
description tag and ranking

Order of Execution

  1. Client call preupload API
    • call s3 to get presigned URL
    • create entry for an image in sql db.
  2. Client call S3 API to upload the actual image.
  3. Use S3 event notification.
    • Update the status of image in sql database.
    • Add an event to queue for transformation.
  4. Transform job is running continuously.
    • Consume the events and transform the images using image processing libraries.
    • Upload the processed images to S3
    • Update the SQL database to available.
